title: Will Brinson & the 3rd annual NFC South QB rankings
itunes:title: Will Brinson & the 3rd annual NFC South QB rankings
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 by Handsome Hank and on Skype by CBS Sports' Will Brinson for their 3rd annual NFC South QB rankings. First, the guys get into if the Browns should have drafted Bradley Chubb over Denzel Ward after Gregg Williams' comments (18:00). Next, Dave asks which 2018 off-season narrative will go away once the regular season starts up (23:55) and if Odell Beckham Jr. is the biggest Jenga piece in the NFL who is next (31:55)? Will declares the Atlanta Falcons his SB LIII champion while Dave says they will be at least a top 3 NFC team (50:30). Finally, Shek and Will list their 2018 NFC South QB rankings both having the same quarterback in the #1 spot.
